author: Elliot Njus | The Oregonian/OregonLive
title: TriMet ticket machines not processing bank cards
text:
Technical problems may complicate the Friday morning commute for TriMet commuters.
The agency said just before 9 a.m. its ticket machines weren't processing bank cards.
It suggested using cash or the TriMet Tickets app to pay for a fare, or waiting 15 minutes to see if a fix takes effect.

-- Elliot Njus
